rules.name: Rules Text
rules.text:
{fontsize-12}Changeling {i}(This card is every creature type.){/i}{/fontsize-12}
{fontsize-10}When you cast {cardname}, each opponent reveals their hand. You may have {cardname} enter as a copy of any creature revealed this way, except its name is {cardname} and it has changeling. If you don’t, draw a card.{/fontsize-12}
